# 從頭再嚟  
(pos:成語 / 動詞短語)  
<explanation>  
yue:從最開始嘅地方重新開始，重新做過（通常係因為之前做錯、失敗或唔滿意）（量詞：次）  
eng:to start all over again from the beginning (usually because of failure or dissatisfaction)  

<eg>  
yue:呢份報告寫得一塌糊塗，不如從頭再嚟一次啦！  
(lung4 tau4 zoi3 lai4 jat1 ci3!)  
eng:This report’s a mess — let’s start all over again!  

yue:我哋嘅計劃失敗咗，不如從頭再嚟，呢次一定做得更好。  
(jin4 ci3 ding6 wui6 dou6 zaam3 hou2!)  
eng:Our plan failed — let’s start from scratch; this time we’ll do it better.  

yue:你個蛋糕燒曬咗？唔緊要，我哋從頭再嚟一次，呢次加多啲牛油！  
(jin4 ci3 gaa1 do1 di1 ngau4 jau4!)  
eng:Your cake burnt? Don’t worry — let’s start again, and this time add more butter! [end of text]


